---
import { ArrowRight, GraduationCap } from '@lucide/astro';
---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-surface hero-pattern opacity-50 -z-10"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-12 translate-x-1/3 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary border border-primary/20 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-6">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></span>
            Penerimaan Santri 2026
          </div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="animate-on-scroll delay-100 text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold leading-tight text-secondary mb-4">
          <span class="sr-only">Pondok Pesantren THOLABIE CIBS: </span>
          Menjembatani <span class="text-primary italic font-serif">Iman</span>, Ilmu, dan Karier Masa Depan.
        </h1>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-200 mb-6 flex flex-col items-start gap-2">
          <p class="font-arabic text-2xl text-primary/80 leading-relaxed text-right w-full" dir="rtl">
            يَرْفَعِ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا مِنكُمْ وَالَّذِينَ أُوتُوا الْعِلْمَ دَرَجَاتٍ
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic border-l-2 border-accent pl-2">
            "...Allah akan meninggikan orang-orang yang beriman di antaramu dan orang-orang yang diberi ilmu pengetahuan beberapa derajat..." (QS. Al-Mujadilah: 11)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:hidden relative w-full aspect-[4/5] sm:aspect-square rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl animate-on-scroll delay-200 mb-8 mt-2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-secondary/20 mix-blend-multiply z-10 transition-opacity hover:opacity-0 duration-500"></div>
          <img
            src="/img/pondok-pesantren-tholabie-malang-cibs.webp"
            alt="Santri Pondok Pesantren THOLABIE CIBS Malang belajar teknologi digital"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 sm:bottom-6 sm:left-6 sm:right-6 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl z-20 flex justify-between items-center border border-white/50 animate-float">
            <div>
              <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">
                Mitra Pendidikan Formal
              </p>
              <p class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm sm:text-lg">Politeknik Kota Malang</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0">
              <GraduationCap class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 h-6" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="animate-on-scroll delay-300 text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Pendidikan asrama Islami modern yang terintegrasi dengan beasiswa penuh politeknik dan pelatihan intensif keahlian digital. Menyiapkan generasi Muslim berakhlaqul karimah untuk memimpin ekonomi digital.
        </p>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll delay-400 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/6285183003060"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold rounded-full text-primary-dark bg-accent hover:bg-accent-light transition-all shadow-premium hover:shadow-premium-hover hover:-translate-y-0.5 group"
          >
            Hubungi via WhatsApp
            <ArrowRight class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
          </a>
          <a
            href="#beasiswa"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold rounded-full text-primary border-2 border-primary/20 hover:border-primary hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all"
          >
            Lihat Program Beasiswa
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden lg:block relative lg:ml-auto w-full max-w-lg aspect-[4/5] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl animate-on-scroll delay-200">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-secondary/20 mix-blend-multiply z-10 transition-opacity hover:opacity-0 duration-500"></div>
        <img
          src="/img/pondok-pesantren-tholabie-malang-cibs.webp"
          alt="Santri Pondok Pesantren THOLABIE CIBS Malang belajar teknologi digital"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl z-20 flex justify-between items-center border border-white/50 animate-float">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Mitra Pendidikan Formal</p>
            <p class="text-secondary font-bold text-lg">Politeknik Kota Malang</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
            <GraduationCap class="w-6 h-6" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
